snippet.title: Prinny Presents NIS Classics Vol. 2 - ZHP Spotlight (Nintendo Switch, PC)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/nis-classics/vol-2/

In ZHP: Unlosing Ranger vs. Darkdeath Evilman, your character is custom-made to kick as—many enemies to the curb as you want! Customize yourself from head to toe, establish a base and work your way through a myriad of maps, each randomly generated and all part of your own unique story!

Prinny Presents NIS Classics Vol. 2 comes to Nintendo Switch on May 10, 2022!

#NISClassics #NISAmerica #MakaiKingdom
